<br>
During the installation of SoL you should received a message which indicated VI recommends you install SoL under the Administrator account or an account with Administrative priviledges.<br>
<br>
The error in question...although I can not find the thread on Microsoft's site, usually deal with NTFS file systems and the adminstrative rights down to the file level.<br>
